{
  "texts": [
    "We detail the hyperparameters for training in Table 5, with a default batch size of 2.",
    "In HotpotQA, we have enriched the action set in previous works (Yao et al., 2023b; Liu et al., 2023b) by incorporating Bing Search as an external knowledge source.",
    "As a result, we now feature four distinct actions within HotpotQA to enhance its functionality and performance: (1) Retrieve[entity]: Retrieve the exact entity on Wikipedia and return the first paragraph if it exists.",
    "If not, return some similar entities for searching.",
    "(2) Search[topic]: Use Bing Search to find relevant information on a specified topic, question, or term."
  ]
}